  ---

  ## Leaders, Killers, Fillers Framework

  How to structure what's **included** in each tier:

  | Type | Definition | Role in Tier |
  |------|------------|--------------|
  | **Killers** | Must-have baseline (table stakes) | Every tier has these |
  | **Leaders** | High-value features that draw them in | Added in higher tiers |
  | **Fillers** | Nice-to-haves that add perceived value | Top tier extras |

  ---

