  ### Leaders/Killers/Fillers by Segment - Summary

  | Segment | Killers (Every Tier) | Leaders (Draw) | Fillers (Extras) |
  |---------|---------------------|----------------|------------------|
  | **BUSY PRO** | Quality, cleanup | Same-week, photo updates, 90-day | Direct line, free small fix |
  | **PROP MGR** | Quality, tenant coord | Priority response, dedicated line, Net 30 | Volume discount, quarterly walk |
  | **SMALL BIZ** | Quality, cleanup, invoicing | After-hours, zero disruption | Same-day, emergency line |
  | **DIY DEFERRER** | Quality, cleanup | Faster scheduling, 30-day guarantee | 90-day, free small fix |
  | **BUDGET** | Quality, cleanup | N/A | N/A |

