  ### Follow-Up Message Templates

  **First Follow-Up (General):**
  > "Hi [Name], just checking in on the quote I sent for [job]. Any questions I can answer? Happy to adjust if needed."

  **First Follow-Up (BUSY PRO):**
  > "Hi [Name], following up on [job]. I've got availability [this week/next few days] if you'd like to lock in a Priority slot."

  **First Follow-Up (PROP MGR):**
  > "Hi [Name], checking in on the quote for [property address]. Let me know if you'd like to discuss the Partner Program for your other properties."

  **First Follow-Up (SMALL BIZ):**
  > "Hi [Name], following up on the quote for [business]. Want me to pencil in an after-hours slot so there's no disruption to your day?"

  **First Follow-Up (DIY DEFERRER):**
  > "Hi [Name], just checking in. Still have that list of jobs? Happy to batch them together whenever you're ready."

  **Final Follow-Up (All):**
  > "Hi [Name], I'll assume you've sorted this out. If things change or you need help down the road, feel free to reach out. All the best!"

  ---

