  ### Phase Transition Criteria

  | Move From | Move To | When |
  |-----------|---------|------|
  | Phase 1 | Phase 2 | Brain can detect segments with 70%+ accuracy |
  | Phase 2 | Phase 3 | Override rate drops below 10%, conversion stable |

